| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4520 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4c982061-9879-5707-9830-a7a05f43b0ca"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
